*Pozadi* su se čuli koraci nekog stranca. (Behind, footsteps of a stranger were heard.)

Nisam videla šta se događa *pozadi* mene. (I didn't see what was happening behind me.)

Šum *pozadine* je bio veoma glasan. (The background noise was very loud.)

Ćutala je u nadi da će sakriti svoje pravo ime iza *pozadine*. (She stayed silent hoping to hide her real name behind the background.)

Čuo se glas koji se činio dalekim i izmišljenim iz *pozadine*. (A voice was heard that sounded far away and made up from the background.)